    InvalidWorkerError

    Implements a runnable that in a new Thread, one for each virtual view, check if the client is connected to the server.
    WinnerNotification
    Implements the message used to announce the winner.
    Worker
    This class manages the workers of a player on the board
    WorkerPositionRequest
    Implements the message to ask a player the start position of specified worker among the available ones.

    Implements the message used to answer to the worker position request by sending the X and Y coordinate on the board.
